    "star": null,
    "review_title": "",
    "body": "It's better to buy products directly from the official website instead of Amazon because Amazon sends used and display items. The packaging is so poor, it looks like someone has opened and inspected it multiple times. I'm going out of town today, so I'm not returning this product. Not recommended. Amazon's products, quality, and services are all terrible.",
