    "brand": "nasher_miles",
    "star": null,
    "review_title": "",
    "body": "It is great in terms of storage and size, wheels are also very smooth, storage expansion also works well, overall it’s great smooth and very practical in terms of usages. Wheels are great and body balance is also great. (Doesn’t tip over) Zipper and locks both are sturdy and easy to use. Just one downside is it’s not scratch proof, it attracts scratches very easily. Don’t take me wrong, if these scratches (shown in the photo) are fine, it’s a great bag. Specially I love its wheels, they are very smooth. Photos are after 4-5 flights.",
    "date_str": "Reviewed in India on 11 January 2026",
